                <h1>Exploring the Culture and Resilience of Haiti</h1>
                <p>Haiti, a Caribbean nation, boasts a rich culture influenced by African, French, and Spanish heritage. Its vibrant art, music, and delicious cuisine reflect its diverse roots. Despite challenges like poverty and natural disasters, Haitians display remarkable resilience and creativity, creating a unique identity amidst adversity.</p>
